{"tid":1141381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［破釜沈舟］屯門創業初嘗試求支持","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T13:20:02.000Z","uid":249339,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1199954483898431005595dc805005122a1e392","tid":1141381,"uid":249339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"小弟同幾個朋友大學畢業膽粗粗係屯門開左間補習社，只為自力更生，見到小朋友進步同時亦一嚐破釜沈舟既滋味。<br />\n<br />\n我地亦發現呢一年幾來我們既小學學生好多在小二小三階段缺乏閱讀，導致語文能力好弱。所以希望透過Facebook網頁定期發放一些對小朋友/學生學習的資訊，包括<br />\n<br />\n逢星期一既學英文系列<br />\n星期三既愛閱讀系列<br />\n星期五既如何學更好系列<br />\n<br />\n來緊亦會星期二四發放中學文言文，寫作，數學解題方面資訊<br />\n<br />\n望各位巴打可以俾個like支持一下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/legendbuilderedu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flegendbuilderedu%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHiIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=0f926c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/legendbuilderedu/</a><br />\n<br />\n絕非推銷，因為我們只做區內生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6c3d6de5904bef024cdd914343ba6d80a93a14","tid":1141381,"uid":70425,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"成篇文章都係推銷<br />\n之後補一句唔係推銷"},{"pid":"c5d5ed22c1bf5fc9c253630c332f486a6353e734","tid":1141381,"uid":247836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ef2ea5948aa746b85ef4153c9afa64c9f08acf6","tid":1141381,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"請連生del po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b20a07de1b8fc2231e23a7474831a97313de85","tid":1141381,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"搞手們只想打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ca0ab9356551d6fc84e854a785787c9746fc25","tid":1141381,"uid":249339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"q